{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So a couple of years ago I started a program"},{"time":3000,"text":"to try to get the rockstar tech and design people"},{"time":7000,"text":"to take a year off"},{"time":9000,"text":"and work in the one environment"},{"time":11000,"text":"that represents pretty much everything they're supposed to hate;"},{"time":14000,"text":"we have them work in government."},{"time":17000,"text":"The program is called Code for America,"},{"time":19000,"text":"and it's a little bit like a Peace Corps for geeks."},{"time":22000,"text":"We select a few fellows every year"},{"time":25000,"text":"and we have them work with city governments."},{"time":28000,"text":"Instead of sending them off into the Third World,"},{"time":31000,"text":"we send them into the wilds of City Hall."},{"time":33000,"text":"And there they make great apps, they work with city staffers."},{"time":36000,"text":"But really what they're doing is they're showing what's possible"},{"time":39000,"text":"with technology today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"So meet Al."},{"time":43000,"text":"Al is a fire hydrant in the city of Boston."},{"time":45000,"text":"Here it kind of looks like he's looking for a date,"},{"time":48000,"text":"but what he's really looking for is for someone to shovel him out when he gets snowed in,"},{"time":51000,"text":"because he knows he's not very good at fighting fires"},{"time":53000,"text":"when he's covered in four feet of snow."},{"time":56000,"text":"Now how did he come to be looking for help"},{"time":58000,"text":"in this very unique manner?"},{"time":60000,"text":"We had a team of fellows in Boston last year"},{"time":62000,"text":"through the Code for America program."},{"time":64000,"text":"They were there in February, and it snowed a lot in February last year."},{"time":67000,"text":"And they noticed that the city never gets"},{"time":69000,"text":"to digging out these fire hydrants."},{"time":71000,"text":"But one fellow in particular,"},{"time":73000,"text":"a guy named Erik Michaels-Ober,"},{"time":75000,"text":"noticed something else,"},{"time":77000,"text":"and that's that citizens are shoveling out sidewalks"},{"time":79000,"text":"right in front of these things."},{"time":81000,"text":"So he did what any good developer would do,"},{"time":83000,"text":"he wrote an app."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85000,"text":"It's a cute little app where you can adopt a fire hydrant."},{"time":87000,"text":"So you agree to dig it out when it snows."},{"time":89000,"text":"If you do, you get to name it,"},{"time":91000,"text":"and he called the first one Al."},{"time":93000,"text":"And if you don't, someone can steal it from you."},{"time":95000,"text":"So it's got cute little game dynamics on it."},{"time":98000,"text":"This is a modest little app."},{"time":100000,"text":"It's probably the smallest"},{"time":102000,"text":"of the 21 apps that the fellows wrote last year."},{"time":104000,"text":"But it's doing something"},{"time":106000,"text":"that no other government technology does."},{"time":108000,"text":"It's spreading virally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111000,"text":"There's a guy in the I.T. department of the City of Honolulu"},{"time":114000,"text":"who saw this app and realized"},{"time":116000,"text":"that he could use it, not for snow,"},{"time":118000,"text":"but to get citizens to adopt tsunami sirens."},{"time":122000,"text":"It's very important that these tsunami sirens work,"},{"time":124000,"text":"but people steal the batteries out of them."},{"time":126000,"text":"So he's getting citizens to check on them."},{"time":128000,"text":"And then Seattle decided to use it"},{"time":131000,"text":"to get citizens to clear out clogged storm drains."},{"time":134000,"text":"And Chicago just rolled it out"},{"time":136000,"text":"to get people to sign up to shovel sidewalks when it snows."},{"time":139000,"text":"So we now know of nine cities"},{"time":141000,"text":"that are planning to use this."},{"time":143000,"text":"And this has spread just frictionlessly,"},{"time":145000,"text":"organically, naturally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147000,"text":"If you know anything about government technology,"},{"time":149000,"text":"you know that this isn't how it normally goes."},{"time":153000,"text":"Procuring software usually takes a couple of years."},{"time":156000,"text":"We had a team that worked on a project in Boston last year"},{"time":159000,"text":"that took three people about two and a half months."},{"time":162000,"text":"It was a way that parents could figure out"},{"time":164000,"text":"which were the right public schools for their kids."},{"time":166000,"text":"We were told afterward that if that had gone through normal channels,"},{"time":169000,"text":"it would have taken at least two years"},{"time":172000,"text":"and it would have cost about two million dollars."},{"time":175000,"text":"And that's nothing."},{"time":177000,"text":"There is one project in the California court system right now"},{"time":179000,"text":"that so far cost taxpayers"},{"time":181000,"text":"two billion dollars,"},{"time":183000,"text":"and it doesn't work."},{"time":185000,"text":"And there are projects like this"},{"time":187000,"text":"at every level of government."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189000,"text":"So an app that takes a couple of days to write"},{"time":193000,"text":"and then spreads virally,"},{"time":195000,"text":"that's sort of a shot across the bow"},{"time":197000,"text":"to the institution of government."},{"time":199000,"text":"It suggests how government could work better --"},{"time":201000,"text":"not more like a private company,"},{"time":203000,"text":"as many people think it should."},{"time":205000,"text":"And not even like a tech company,"},{"time":207000,"text":"but more like the Internet itself."},{"time":210000,"text":"And that means permissionless,"},{"time":212000,"text":"it means open, it means generative."},{"time":216000,"text":"And that's important."},{"time":218000,"text":"But what's more important about this app"},{"time":220000,"text":"is that it represents how a new generation"},{"time":222000,"text":"is tackling the problem of government --"},{"time":225000,"text":"not as the problem of an ossified institution,"},{"time":228000,"text":"but as a problem of collective action."},{"time":230000,"text":"And that's great news,"},{"time":232000,"text":"because, it turns out, we're very good at collective action"},{"time":235000,"text":"with digital technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"Now there's a very large community of people"},{"time":239000,"text":"that are building the tools that we need"},{"time":241000,"text":"to do things together effectively."},{"time":243000,"text":"It's not just Code for America fellows,"},{"time":245000,"text":"there are hundreds of people all over the country"},{"time":247000,"text":"that are standing and writing civic apps"},{"time":249000,"text":"every day in their own communities."},{"time":253000,"text":"They haven't given up on government."},{"time":255000,"text":"They are frustrated as hell with it,"},{"time":257000,"text":"but they're not complaining about it,"},{"time":259000,"text":"they're fixing it."},{"time":261000,"text":"And these folks know something"},{"time":263000,"text":"that we've lost sight of."},{"time":265000,"text":"And that's that when you strip away all your feelings"},{"time":267000,"text":"about politics and the line at the DMV"},{"time":269000,"text":"and all those other things"},{"time":271000,"text":"that we're really mad about,"},{"time":273000,"text":"government is, at its core,"},{"time":276000,"text":"in the words of Tim O'Reilly,"},{"time":278000,"text":"\"What we do together that we can't do alone.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":283000,"text":"Now a lot of people have given up on government."},{"time":285000,"text":"And if you're one of those people,"},{"time":287000,"text":"I would ask that you reconsider,"},{"time":290000,"text":"because things are changing."},{"time":292000,"text":"Politics is not changing;"},{"time":295000,"text":"government is changing."},{"time":297000,"text":"And because government"},{"time":299000,"text":"ultimately derives its power from us --"},{"time":301000,"text":"remember \"We the people?\" --"},{"time":303000,"text":"how we think about it"},{"time":305000,"text":"is going to effect how that change happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"Now I didn't know very much about government when I started this program."},{"time":311000,"text":"And like a lot of people,"},{"time":313000,"text":"I thought government was basically about getting people elected to office."},{"time":316000,"text":"Well after two years, I've come to the conclusion"},{"time":318000,"text":"that, especially local government,"},{"time":320000,"text":"is about opossums."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"This is the call center for the services and information line."},{"time":326000,"text":"It's generally where you will get"},{"time":328000,"text":"if you call 311 in your city."},{"time":330000,"text":"If you should ever have the chance"},{"time":332000,"text":"to staff your city's call center,"},{"time":334000,"text":"as our fellow Scott Silverman did as part of the program --"},{"time":336000,"text":"in fact, they all do that --"},{"time":338000,"text":"you will find that people call government"},{"time":341000,"text":"with a very wide range of issues,"},{"time":343000,"text":"including having an opossum stuck in your house."},{"time":346000,"text":"So Scott gets this call."},{"time":348000,"text":"He types \"Opossum\" into this official knowledge base."},{"time":350000,"text":"He doesn't really come up with anything. He starts with animal control."},{"time":353000,"text":"And finally, he says, \"Look, can you just open all the doors to your house"},{"time":356000,"text":"and play music really loud"},{"time":358000,"text":"and see if the thing leaves?\""},{"time":360000,"text":"So that worked. So booya for Scott."},{"time":363000,"text":"But that wasn't the end of the opossums."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365000,"text":"Boston doesn't just have a call center."},{"time":367000,"text":"It has an app, a Web and mobile app,"},{"time":369000,"text":"called Citizens Connect."},{"time":371000,"text":"Now we didn't write this app."},{"time":373000,"text":"This is the work of the very smart people"},{"time":375000,"text":"at the Office of New Urban Mechanics in Boston."},{"time":377000,"text":"So one day -- this is an actual report -- this came in:"},{"time":380000,"text":"\"Opossum in my trashcan. Can't tell if it's dead."},{"time":383000,"text":"How do I get this removed?\""},{"time":386000,"text":"But what happens with Citizens Connect is different."},{"time":388000,"text":"So Scott was speaking person-to-person."},{"time":391000,"text":"But on Citizens Connect everything is public,"},{"time":393000,"text":"so everybody can see this."},{"time":395000,"text":"And in this case, a neighbor saw it."},{"time":397000,"text":"And the next report we got said,"},{"time":399000,"text":"\"I walked over to this location,"},{"time":401000,"text":"found the trashcan behind the house."},{"time":403000,"text":"Opossum? Check. Living? Yep."},{"time":406000,"text":"Turned trashcan on its side. Walked home."},{"time":408000,"text":"Goodnight sweet opossum.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":410000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":412000,"text":"Pretty simple."},{"time":414000,"text":"So this is great. This is the digital meeting the physical."},{"time":417000,"text":"And it's also a great example"},{"time":419000,"text":"of government getting in on the crowd-sourcing game."},{"time":422000,"text":"But it's also a great example of government as a platform."},{"time":425000,"text":"And I don't mean necessarily"},{"time":427000,"text":"a technological definition of platform here."},{"time":429000,"text":"I'm just talking about a platform for people"},{"time":431000,"text":"to help themselves and to help others."},{"time":435000,"text":"So one citizen helped another citizen,"},{"time":437000,"text":"but government played a key role here."},{"time":439000,"text":"It connected those two people."},{"time":442000,"text":"And it could have connected them with government services if they'd been needed,"},{"time":445000,"text":"but a neighbor is a far better and cheaper alternative"},{"time":448000,"text":"to government services."},{"time":450000,"text":"When one neighbor helps another,"},{"time":452000,"text":"we strengthen our communities."},{"time":454000,"text":"We call animal control, it just costs a lot of money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459000,"text":"Now one of the important things we need to think about government"},{"time":461000,"text":"is that it's not the same thing as politics."},{"time":464000,"text":"And most people get that,"},{"time":466000,"text":"but they think that one is the input to the other."},{"time":469000,"text":"That our input to the system of government"},{"time":471000,"text":"is voting."},{"time":473000,"text":"Now how many times have we elected a political leader --"},{"time":475000,"text":"and sometimes we spend a lot of energy"},{"time":477000,"text":"getting a new political leader elected --"},{"time":480000,"text":"and then we sit back and we expect government"},{"time":482000,"text":"to reflect our values and meet our needs,"},{"time":486000,"text":"and then not that much changes?"},{"time":490000,"text":"That's because government is like a vast ocean"},{"time":493000,"text":"and politics is the six-inch layer on top."},{"time":497000,"text":"And what's under that"},{"time":499000,"text":"is what we call bureaucracy."},{"time":501000,"text":"And we say that word with such contempt."},{"time":504000,"text":"But it's that contempt"},{"time":506000,"text":"that keeps this thing that we own"},{"time":509000,"text":"and we pay for"},{"time":511000,"text":"as something that's working against us, this other thing,"},{"time":514000,"text":"and then we're disempowering ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517000,"text":"People seem to think politics is sexy."},{"time":520000,"text":"If we want this institution to work for us,"},{"time":523000,"text":"we're going to have to make bureaucracy sexy."},{"time":526000,"text":"Because that's where the real work of government happens."},{"time":530000,"text":"We have to engage with the machinery of government."},{"time":533000,"text":"So that's OccupytheSEC movement has done."},{"time":535000,"text":"Have you seen these guys?"},{"time":537000,"text":"It's a group of concerned citizens"},{"time":539000,"text":"that have written a very detailed"},{"time":541000,"text":"325-page report"},{"time":543000,"text":"that's a response to the SEC's request for comment"},{"time":545000,"text":"on the Financial Reform Bill."},{"time":547000,"text":"That's not being politically active,"},{"time":549000,"text":"that's being bureaucratically active."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553000,"text":"Now for those of us who've given up on government,"},{"time":556000,"text":"it's time that we asked ourselves"},{"time":558000,"text":"about the world that we want to leave for our children."},{"time":561000,"text":"You have to see the enormous challenges"},{"time":563000,"text":"that they're going to face."},{"time":566000,"text":"Do we really think we're going to get where we need to go"},{"time":569000,"text":"without fixing the one institution"},{"time":571000,"text":"that can act on behalf of all of us?"},{"time":573000,"text":"We can't do without government,"},{"time":575000,"text":"but we do need it"},{"time":577000,"text":"to be more effective."},{"time":579000,"text":"The good news is that technology is making it possible"},{"time":581000,"text":"to fundamentally reframe"},{"time":583000,"text":"the function of government"},{"time":585000,"text":"in a way that can actually scale"},{"time":588000,"text":"by strengthening civil society."},{"time":590000,"text":"And there's a generation out there that's grown up on the Internet,"},{"time":593000,"text":"and they know that it's not that hard"},{"time":595000,"text":"to do things together,"},{"time":597000,"text":"you just have to architect the systems the right way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":601000,"text":"Now the average age of our fellows is 28,"},{"time":604000,"text":"so I am, begrudgingly,"},{"time":606000,"text":"almost a generation older than most of them."},{"time":609000,"text":"This is a generation"},{"time":611000,"text":"that's grown up taking their voices pretty much for granted."},{"time":614000,"text":"They're not fighting that battle that we're all fighting"},{"time":616000,"text":"about who gets to speak;"},{"time":618000,"text":"they all get to speak."},{"time":620000,"text":"They can express their opinion"},{"time":622000,"text":"on any channel at any time,"},{"time":624000,"text":"and they do."},{"time":626000,"text":"So when they're faced with the problem of government,"},{"time":629000,"text":"they don't care as much"},{"time":631000,"text":"about using their voices."},{"time":633000,"text":"They're using their hands."},{"time":635000,"text":"They're using their hands"},{"time":637000,"text":"to write applications that make government work better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":640000,"text":"And those applications let us use our hands"},{"time":643000,"text":"to make our communities better."},{"time":646000,"text":"That could be shoveling out a hydrant, pulling a weed,"},{"time":649000,"text":"turning over a garbage can with an opossum in it."},{"time":653000,"text":"And certainly, we could have been shoveling out those fire hydrants all along,"},{"time":656000,"text":"and many people do."},{"time":658000,"text":"But these apps are like little digital reminders"},{"time":661000,"text":"that we're not just consumers,"},{"time":663000,"text":"and we're not just consumers of government,"},{"time":665000,"text":"putting in our taxes and getting back services."},{"time":668000,"text":"We're more than that,"},{"time":670000,"text":"we're citizens."},{"time":672000,"text":"And we're not going to fix government"},{"time":675000,"text":"until we fix citizenship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":678000,"text":"So the question I have for all of you here:"},{"time":682000,"text":"When it comes to the big, important things"},{"time":684000,"text":"that we need to do together,"},{"time":686000,"text":"all of us together,"},{"time":688000,"text":"are we just going to be a crowd of voices,"},{"time":691000,"text":"or are we also going to be"},{"time":693000,"text":"a crowd of hands?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":695000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}